Text: REI think we are OK with switchyard issues for now Thanks John Original Message From mailto Sent Monday October PM To tilicorpcom Cc Subject John We are trying to set up a meeting tomorrow to discuss the Wheatland switchyard issues We will have someone from legal Mitch Robinson and Don Miller attending for Enron Please let me know what time works best for you for tomorrow morning Thanks Ben Rogers
